表格用户表的代码预览

drop table if exists t_user;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: t_user */
/*==============================================================*/
create table t_user
(
id integer(20),
login_name varchar(100),
login_password varchar(100),
nick_name varchar(100),
real_name varchar(50),
department_id integer(20),
create_time datetime,
update_time datetime,
create_user integer(20),
update_user integer(20),
head_icon varchar(100),
region_id integer(20)
);

alter table t_user add constraint FK_Reference_2 foreign key (id)
references 部门表 (id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
